1
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,880
Come on, Dad.

2
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,280
Slow down.

3
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,360
This magic trick

4
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,520
was originally created by our family.

5
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:07,280
I also rigged

6
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:09,039
this floor.

7
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:12,640
After Xiaomei enters the wooden box and closes the door,

8
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:15,240
she can use the mechanism on the floor

9
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,940
to enter the secret passage under the platform.

10
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:20,400
Once she safely goes down into the passage,

11
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:24,120
she places the prepared cat on the floor

12
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:26,040
and closes the mechanism.

13
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:29,920
This way, a person can turn into any object.

14
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,480
When this wooden box

15
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:35,400
has made a full rotation,

16
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,920
Xiaomei

17
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:41,320
uses the same method to lift herself back up.

18
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,840
This way, the cat turns back into Xiaomei.

19
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,440
So, where does the other end

20
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,040
of this secret passage lead?

21
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,880
Behind the curtain.

22
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,079
After Xiaomei entered the secret passage,

23
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,920
she was ambushed by the suspect.

24
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,240
Because the audience around was too noisy,

25
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,800
we didn't hear Xiaomei's cries for help.

26
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,210
Xiaomei fainted from blood loss or shock.

27
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:13,780
The suspect then took Xiaomei onto a carriage and fled.

28
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:18,410
Based on the note next to the severed limb,

29
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:21,360
it's likely Xiaomei was kidnapped by bandits.

30
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:25,200
But why would the bandit cut off her arm on the spot?

31
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,920
She probably resisted.

32
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,280
And being pressed for time,

33
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,720
the person harmed her.

34
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,720
Such a villain,

35
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:35,040
I will definitely bring him to justice.

36
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,320
Troupe Leader Lu, everyone.

37
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:39,120
We have conducted some investigations.

38
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:41,520
We will certainly get to the bottom of this.

39
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,840
I beg you, officers.

40
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:46,920
Please, you must save my daughter.

41
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:49,200
Even if we have to spend all our savings,

42
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,520
we will save her.

43
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,400
I beg you.

44
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,560
Please get up.

45
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,160
But right now, the kidnappers

46
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,160
haven't left any valid clues for a trade.

47
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,120
We can only wait for now.

48
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,440
I beg you.

49
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,760
Troupe Leader Lu.

50
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,200
Where do you usually live?

51
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,000
Our acrobatics troupe

52
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:09,320
lives right here in this big courtyard.

53
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,840
If the kidnappers come now

54
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,720
and see all of us constables here,

55
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,980
they definitely won't dare to approach.

56
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,600
Have them all change into plain clothes later,

57
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,800
then stake out near the Lu family courtyard.

58
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,720
We will wait for them to come to us.

59
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,620
Okay, I'll arrange it right away.

60
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,520
Rise and shine. Who is it?

61
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,240
Jueming.

62
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,560
Here you are.

63
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,360
Here,

64
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,920
put it here.

65
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,520
These are dishes from Weimanju.

66
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,320
I specially had them delivered.

67
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,440
Try some.

68
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,880
This is too much. I can't finish it by myself.

69
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,320
How about we share some with Master Lu?

70
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,760
And for the brothers outside.

71
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,880
These are all prepared for them.

72
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,880
Please help take them over.

73
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,920
Thanks for your hard work.

74
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,800
It's nothing.

75
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,160
You haven't slept all night.

76
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,720
Skip the noodles.

77
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,860
Have a bowl of beef.

78
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,360
Hold out your hand.

79
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,360
Hold out your hand.

80
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,200
Close your eyes.

81
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:46,820
Did you also learn magic tricks at the Lu Troupe?

82
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,000
Guess

83
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,200
what it is.

84
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,240
A family heirloom.

85
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,200
A bone.

86
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,120
I can't guess.

87
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,280
Isn't this what I saw yesterday?

88
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,200
I saw you liked it yesterday,

89
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,760
so I bought it.

90
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,640
Do you like it?

91
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,560
I like it.

92
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,360
It's very thoughtful of you.

93
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,360
I'm glad you like it.

94
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,680
This is

95
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:48,560
other than what my father gave me,

96
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,120
the best gift I've ever received.

97
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,720
Why?

98
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,080
Mr. Lu,

99
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,450
no matter how I persuade him, he won't eat.

100
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,080
Make some room for me.

101
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,880
You know, no matter how anxious he is,

102
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,360
he shouldn't skip meals entirely, right?

103
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,800
Why aren't you eating?

104
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,000
I'm watching you eat.

105
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,600
Looking at you makes me full.

106
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,800
Tell me,

107
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,960
the Lu Family Troupe is so popular,

108
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,160
and their performances have always gone smoothly.

109
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,220
They usually perform every few days.

110
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:26,500
Why did he suddenly announce the final show yesterday?

111
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,560
Then let me tell you.

112
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,920
Because besides Xiaomei, Troupe Leader Lu

113
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,480
also had an eldest daughter

114
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,680
named Lu Yue.

115
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,960
But she had a terminal illness.

116
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,880
To treat her illness, Troupe Leader Lu

117
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,720
spent all his savings.

118
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,080
But unfortunately,

119
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,360
Yueyue

120
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,600
still passed away.

121
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,680
Troupe Leader Lu was deeply devastated

122
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,840
and wanted to return to the countryside to recover.

123
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,520
But at this crucial moment,

124
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,620
something also happened to Xiaomei.

125
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,280
That's strange.

126
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:01,120
Kidnappers usually target children of wealthy merchants and high officials

127
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,880
to demand a high ransom.

128
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:06,200
But Master Lu doesn't look like a rich man at all.

129
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,610
Why would they kidnap Xiaomei?

130
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,760
If it's not for money,

131
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,360
it must be a personal grudge.

132
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,120
A grudge?

133
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,370
What kind of grudge?

134
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,160
How should I know?

135
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,640
Then go find out.

136
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,520
Right.

137
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,700
Go check. Go check.

138
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:28,210
Take this for them to eat. Go check.

139
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,120
What did you just say?

140
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,039
I said,

141
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:39,280
if they're not after money,

142
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,280
then they have other motives.

143
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,559
No, I mean,

144
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,520
you just

145
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:45,490
said this is the favorite gift you've ever received.

146
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,000
Why is that?

147
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:52,940
Because...

148
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,480
There's news.

149
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,320
I...

150
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,400
There's news.

151
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,160
What are you two talking about?

152
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,960
Nothing.

153
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,680
What is it? What news?

154
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,160
We need to go to the Guan family immediately.

155
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,160
Which Guan family?

156
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,160
Guan Shan, the richest man in Luoyang.

157
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:07,920
His youngest grandson's funeral is today.

158
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,640
But his servants found in his coffin

159
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:12,640
that his young grandson was holding a left arm with both hands,

160
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:15,120
and there was a bamboo strip in his hand.

161
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:50,280
Inside the coffin is the body of an eight-year-old boy.

162
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:54,640
A woman's severed left arm was placed on his chest.

163
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:58,720
There were also bamboo slips with writings on them.

164
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,520
Okay.

165
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,160
Jueming.

166
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:15,420
Auspicious beasts of the ancient dynasty show their majesty.

167
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:18,570
Auspicious birds of this year dance in splendid colors.

168
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:24,040
Who was the first to find

169
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,890
the remains inside the coffin?

170
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,400
It was me.

171
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,080
These past few days,

172
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,880
I have been keeping vigil for the Eldest Young Master.

173
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,480
I was so tired last night

174
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,780
that I fell asleep without realizing it.

175
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,920
When I woke up this morning,

176
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,560
I didn't notice it at first.

177
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,760
I wanted to burn incense,

178
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,840
but I found the coffin lid was not closed properly.

179
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,440
I took a look inside

180
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:58,040
and saw this severed limb placed on his chest.

181
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,840
So you didn't notice

182
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,520
who moved the coffin

183
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:03,160
and put the severed limbs in.

184
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:06,920
Who?

185
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:09,240
Who moved my grandson's coffin?

186
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,400
Who?

187
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:11,960
Master Guan.

188
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,880
I didn't

189
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,400
see it.

190
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,240
You useless thing!

191
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,540
I'll kick you to death!

192
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,480
I'll kick you to death!

193
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,480
Stop hitting him!

194
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,000
Even if he is your servant,

195
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,400
you can't hit him.

196
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:26,040
Besides, he's not the one who moved your grandson's coffin.

197
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:26,920
Who are you?

198
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,920
She is Li...

199
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,040
Let me do it.

200
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,000
I am

201
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,320
the coroner of the magistrate's office.

202
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,520
I heard that in your grandson's coffin,

203
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,960
severed limbs were placed,

204
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:41,600
so I came with Constable Su to investigate.

205
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,200
How do you know he didn't do it?

206
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,920
Look at him.

207
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,960
This servant

208
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,360
has lifeless eyes,

209
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,480
is as timid as a mouse,

210
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,560
and weak.

211
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,440
If he tampered with the coffin

212
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,520
and put limbs in it,

213
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:56,400
he would have run away long ago.

214
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,530
Would he still be here waiting for you?

215
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:01,840
You are quite eloquent, Miss.

216
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,640
Then tell me, who did it?

217
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,600
A group of bandits.

218
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:12,880
Last night, they went to the Lu Troupe and kidnapped the youngest Lu sister.

219
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:15,560
A severed right arm was left at the scene,

220
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,120
along with a note.

221
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:19,120
I suspect it's the same group.

222
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,320
You are saying

223
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:24,080
that the youngest sister of the Lu Troupe was kidnapped?

224
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,280
Master Guan.

225
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,680
Master, are you alright?

226
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,760
Master.

227
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,880
No, why did mentioning my younger sister

228
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:35,080
make him like this?

229
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:36,480
Little sister

230
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:39,100
is the master's biological granddaughter.

231
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,560
Master.

232
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:42,120
Are you alright?

233
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,960
It seems the poem on this bamboo strip

234
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,200
has another meaning.

235
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,840
Think carefully.

236
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,880
Have you seen this handwriting before?

237
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:54,600
I haven't.

238
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:55,440
No.

239
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,960
You don't know this, but

240
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:59,880
although Master Guan is destined for wealth,

241
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:02,680
But there were many misfortunes in his family,

242
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,880
and his children passed away early one after another.

243
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:07,340
His little grandson was the apple of his eye,

244
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:09,960
but he suffered from a brain disease half a year ago

245
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,920
and has been bedridden all day.

246
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:15,680
That night, when I came back from getting medicine for the young master,

247
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:17,960
I saw the Lu Troupe performing on the way.

248
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,640
I happened to glance over

249
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,880
and saw the female illusionist on stage

250
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,880
had a birthmark on her face.

251
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:27,690
This was exactly the same as Master Guan's lost granddaughter.

252
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,610
I hurriedly asked for details.

253
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,880
Boss Lu told me

254
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,280
that he indeed found Xiaomei.

255
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,240
I asked,

256
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,960
and the time and place she was found

257
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,960
matched perfectly with the little granddaughter.

258
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:41,440
I then hurried back to tell Master Guan this news.

259
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,840
After several confirmations,

260
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,720
we finally made sure

261
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:48,360
that Xiaomei of the Lu family is my Master Guan's biological granddaughter.

262
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:51,120
Coincidentally, the young master passed away,

263
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:53,040
leaving the Guan family without an heir.

264
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:56,040
Master Guan just wanted to bring Xiaomei back home.

265
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:58,400
To repay the Lu Troupe for raising her,

266
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:01,160
Master Guan offered three chests of jewelry.

267
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:04,000
The exchange would happen after the young master's funeral.

268
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,920
Unexpectedly,

269
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,360
before he could bring Xiaomei home,

270
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:10,160
this incident occurred.

271
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,200
No wonder they kidnapped Xiaomei.

272
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:14,400
You must have leaked the news.

273
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:17,320
They weren't targeting the Lu Troupe at all.

274
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,000
Officer, this...

275
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,960
I'm not an officer.

276
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,040
I'm a coroner.

277
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,280
Officer Su,

278
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,320
he is the officer.

279
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,080
Officer.

280
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,960
With just this severed hand,

281
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:31,360
how can you be sure it's Xiaomei?

282
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:34,160
When Xiaomei was performing on stage yesterday,

283
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,240
we were all there

284
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:37,340
and witnessed how she was kidnapped.

285
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:40,520
Judging from the bloodstains at the scene and the condition of the severed hand,

286
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,520
it is exactly Xiaomei's right hand.

287
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:46,400
The two severed arms,

288
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,720
and the attached bamboo strips,

289
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,120
have the same handwriting.

290
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,980
They were done by the same person.

291
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,800
Then hurry up and find her!

292
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,880
Did the bandits mention money?

293
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:58,000
My Master Guan is the richest man in the city.

294
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,440
He can afford it.

295
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,640
As long as the young lady's life is spared,

296
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:04,680
don't let them hurt her!

297
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,800
The key to the problem is that

298
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:09,400
the bandits haven't sent any messages.

299
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,360
It looks like

300
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,080
we have news now.

301
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,000
Give it to me.

302
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,960
The location where they want to trade

303
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,760
It's already hidden in the poem.

304
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:25,080
The last two lines on this first bamboo slip

305
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,080
say that

306
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,040
if we want to ransom our little sister,

307
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,640
we need a chest of jewels.

308
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,080
As for the previous line,

309
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:33,800
it seems to say she is in grave danger,

310
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:36,520
but it's actually a riddle.

311
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,080
I understand.

312
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:43,000
'Heaven and earth are separated,

313
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:45,560
Yin and Yang are parted.'

314
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,520
This refers to a location.

315
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:49,240
The location is

316
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,160
a mourning hall.

317
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:54,840
But there are so many mourning halls.

318
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,800
How do we know which one it is?

319
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,680
Right.

320
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,440
This is too complicated.

321
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:01,760
If we can't find it

322
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,000
or guess it,

323
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:05,320
don't these kidnappers want the money?

324
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,360
For them to do this,

325
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,660
there must be a reason.

326
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:13,320
We might as well play their riddle game

327
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:16,480
and see where they will show up.

328
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:25,600
'Auspicious beasts show their majesty.'

329
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,560
A lion.

330
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,840
Speaking of lions,

331
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,960
Fengqi Restaurant on Changle Street opens today.

332
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:35,220
It's a restaurant funded by Master Guan.

333
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,520
There will be a lion dance at the Si hour.

334
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:38,920
Fengqi Restaurant.

335
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:41,600
When did this restaurant appear on Changle Street?

336
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,160
It used to be Wangyue Restaurant.

337
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,960
Boss Zhang couldn't keep it running.

338
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,240
and sold it to Master Guan.

339
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:48,000
So it was renamed Fengqi.

340
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:51,400
Wangyue Restaurant opposite Yichun Brothel has changed its name and owner.

341
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,320
Exactly.

342
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,410
The lion dance at the opening ceremony

343
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,200
matches the riddle perfectly.

344
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,720
Let's set off immediately.

345
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,160
Then pick a few smart constables,

346
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:10,819
bring a box of jewelry, and go to Changle Street.

347
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:11,720
Okay.

348
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:13,960
Brother Su.

349
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:15,730
Please arrange some men

350
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,640
to secretly protect

351
00:17:17,839 --> 00:17:19,880
the Guan residence and Troupe Leader Lu's compound.

352
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:20,240
Okay.

353
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:22,400
I'm worried this bandit is cunning,

354
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:25,760
and this riddle is actually a trap to lure us away.

355
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:26,800
Okay.

356
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,319
You be careful too.

357
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:30,920
Okay.

358
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,640
Jumping so high!

359
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:43,560
Good!

360
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:46,160
Good!

361
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,320
Fengqi Restaurant is really something else.

362
00:17:49,320 --> 00:17:50,160
Yes.

363
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:52,440
Good!

364
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,280
There are too many people here.

365
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:57,120
Be careful.

366
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:57,920
Okay.

367
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,440
Good!

368
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:08,570
Here's another one.

369
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:11,400
Another one.

370
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:13,720
This one is not from Fengqi Restaurant.

371
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,460
Sister Chunyi.

372
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:29,520
Are you and Miss Li here to watch the lion dance?

373
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:30,640
We still have a case.

374
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,200
The child from the theatrical troupe.

375
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,480
Kick his lower body.

376
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:35,580
I'll reward a string of cash for every one knocked down.

377
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:39,440
Did you call this yellow lion?

378
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,920
Haven't you heard?

379
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,280
During a grand opening lion dance,

380
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:44,840
if the lion's head falls to the ground,

381
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,840
it means business will not go well this year.

382
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:48,640
The business will definitely shut down.

383
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,500
Sister Chunyi.

384
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:51,000
Boss, why are you doing this?

385
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,440
Do you hold a grudge against the Guan family?

386
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,520
As you know,

387
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,620
this shop belongs to the Guan family.

388
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:59,800
Although Guan Shan is the richest man,

389
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:02,160
I wish he would drop dead sooner.

390
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,000
Sister Chunyi,

391
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:07,500
how come I didn't know you had a grudge against the Guan family?

392
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:11,080
Actually, very few people know about this.

393
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,160
Actually,

394
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,850
the name Yichun of this Yichun Brothel

395
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,320
doesn't refer to me,

396
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:19,240
but Zhou Yichun.

397
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:23,000
She originally married Guan Shan's eldest son.

398
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,680
But because the baby girl she gave birth to had a birthmark on her face,

399
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,940
Guan Shan considered it an ominous sign,

400
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:29,720
and ordered his servants overnight

401
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,120
to abandon the baby girl.

402
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:34,160
The next day, unable to find her child, Zhou Yichun

403
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:36,160
searched like a madwoman.

404
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,080
Who knew that Guan Shan, this despicable man,

405
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:40,520
would force his eldest son to divorce his wife?

406
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:42,580
Although the eldest son was devoted,

407
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:44,640
he didn't dare to disobey his father's order,

408
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:47,100
and secretly gave Zhou Yichun a sum of money.

409
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,040
Having seen through men, she

410
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:51,200
took the money, left the Guan family,

411
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,480
and opened this Yichun Brothel.

412
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:56,520
When I first came to Luoyang, I met her.

413
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:59,000
Because of our similar names, we became sisters.

414
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,260
Who knew she had depression in her heart.

415
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,970
In less than half a year,

416
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,480
she passed away.

417
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,760
She left this Yichun Brothel to me.

418
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:12,530
Now Guan Shan wants to open a business at my doorstep.

419
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:15,480
Isn't he the most superstitious?

420
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,520
I'll let his lion head fall to the ground,

421
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:18,960
so he can't get a good omen.

422
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,120
Beat it down.

423
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:20,600
Attack!

424
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:22,160
Good.

425
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,200
Good.

426
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,400
Whose yellow lion is this?

427
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,160
Keep fighting.

428
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,770
Nonsense. This is absolute nonsense.

429
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,360
Hey there, why are you causing trouble?

430
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:44,480
I just love causing trouble.

431
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,840
Is it any of your business?

432
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:47,000
There's also a red lion.

433
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,040
Keep fighting.

434
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:51,040
Good.

435
00:20:53,840 --> 00:20:55,440
Fight.

436
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,210
We guessed the wrong place.

437
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:46,760
Where to find such pristine beauty.

438
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,240
Brother Guan.

439
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,360
Vice Governor Li.

440
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,000
Here, Brother Guan.

441
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:05,640
This is the money box found at the Yamen gate at the hour of Si.

442
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,200
Take a look.

443
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:21,320
First they sent the hands to my residence,

444
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:24,000
and then the legs to the Yamen.

445
00:22:24,040 --> 00:22:25,360
These bandits

446
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:26,920
are going too far.

447
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,760
They completely ignore the law.

448
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:29,560
Yes.

449
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:32,600
The thieves are outrageous.

450
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:34,980
They actually openly provoke the Yamen.

451
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:36,720
I will definitely dispatch more men

452
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,040
to search the whole city,

453
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:40,480
arrest the criminals as soon as possible,

454
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:42,120
rescue your granddaughter,

455
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:44,440
and get justice for you, Brother Guan.

456
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:50,040
Without her hands,

457
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:52,040
and missing a leg,

458
00:22:52,080 --> 00:22:53,480
she is no longer whole.

459
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:56,250
What's the point of bringing her back?

460
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,200
What's the point?

461
00:22:58,840 --> 00:23:00,800
Is she just a tool to you?

462
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,040
She is your own granddaughter.

463
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,560
Even if she is disabled,

464
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,720
she is still your own granddaughter.

465
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,520
No wonder when she was born a girl with a facial birthmark,

466
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:12,000
you abandoned her.

467
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:13,120
What did you say,

468
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:13,880
Jinglan?

469
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:14,960
Brother Guan,

470
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,480
my daughter is poorly disciplined.

471
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:18,600
Please forgive her.

472
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:20,080
Am I wrong?

473
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:21,640
If the Guan family's grandson hadn't died of illness

474
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,570
and left no heir,

475
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:25,120
he wouldn't care about his granddaughter's safety at all.

476
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:26,280
Get out!

477
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,680
I... Get out, all of you.

478
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:29,280
No, Father. I...

479
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:30,320
Get out.

480
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:37,080
Su Lang.

481
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:40,960
I promote you to Chief Constable.

482
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,320
Within two hours,

483
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:44,520
find the Guan family's granddaughter,

484
00:23:44,520 --> 00:23:45,840
dead or alive.

485
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:12,800
Don't be angry.

486
00:24:15,560 --> 00:24:17,820
Your father usually dotes on you so much.

487
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,240
He is your father, after all.

488
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:25,920
You argued with him in front of Elder Guan.

489
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,960
And it was at the government office.

490
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,400
He was put on the spot.

491
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,680
Calm down.

492
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:34,040
You heard him just now.

493
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:36,520
He said it himself. He doesn't care about his granddaughter's life

494
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,720
just because she is physically disabled.

495
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:39,960
In his eyes,

496
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:43,280
his granddaughter is just a replacement that could be abandoned before

497
00:24:43,280 --> 00:24:45,320
and called back now.

498
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,160
If I were Xiaomei,

499
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,690
I would want to stay with Troupe Leader Lu too.

500
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:51,080
My dear lady,

501
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:53,320
you've vented your anger,

502
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,760
but I'm doomed.

503
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:58,120
The Deputy Magistrate gave me two hours to solve the case.

504
00:24:58,120 --> 00:25:00,480
Where am I supposed to solve the case?

505
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,840
Take out your riddle and see.

506
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:04,160
What location is it?

507
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:08,840
Thousands of beauties add color,

508
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:11,440
where to seek the powdered jade?

509
00:25:12,080 --> 00:25:13,640
Is it talking about rouge?

510
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,680
If it were really that simple,

511
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:18,800
we wouldn't have made mistakes again and again.

512
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,880
Then why was the previous answer

513
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:23,380
not the lion in front of Fengqi Pavilion?

514
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,120
Look,

515
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:30,680
there are also stone lions at the government office,

516
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,080
which makes sense too.

517
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:36,440
One riddle can have multiple answers.

518
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:38,560
Which one is the correct answer?

519
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:40,440
To get the correct answer,

520
00:25:40,840 --> 00:25:42,240
we need to see someone.

521
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,000
Troupe Leader Lu.

522
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:46,840
Let's go without delay.

523
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,160
Su Lang.

524
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:55,840
I know.

525
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:58,840
If Xiaomei was just a troupe member,

526
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,200
she wouldn't have been kidnapped.

527
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:02,760
It's exactly because someone learned she was a member of the Guan family

528
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:04,520
that she encountered the bandits.

529
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,840
The people in this troupe know about the secret passages

530
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:09,760
and could immediately find out Xiaomei's true identity.

531
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,960
They fit all the criteria for a suspect.

532
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:14,560
The people in the troupe have no motive.

533
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,320
Think about it.

534
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:18,000
They could have just taken a healthy Xiaomei to the Guan family for ransom.

535
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,800
Why go to all this extra trouble?

536
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:42,800
Troupe Leader Lu.

537
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,240
I'm coming.

538
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:50,720
Did you find Xiaomei?

539
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,040
No.

540
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,080
Mr. Lu,

541
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:56,440
we came here today to find out about Xiaomei.

542
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,560
You said

543
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,640
you were the one who found Xiaomei back then?

544
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,440
No, no.

545
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,940
My youngest son found her.

546
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:08,720
Brother, brother.

547
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:21,320
When we first found the child,

548
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:23,040
she was less than a year old.

549
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:24,960
Just a baby like this.

550
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,660
Right here on her right cheek,

551
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,720
she had a red birthmark.

552
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,600
Everyone asked around,

553
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:32,760
"Whose lost child is this?"

554
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:36,160
After three or four days, there was no news at all.

555
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,440
So everyone guessed

556
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:41,920
this must be an abandoned baby.

557
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:44,900
Our theater troupe travels everywhere to perform.

558
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,560
Leave her behind?

559
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:48,320
How could we bear to do that?

560
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:49,800
Then everyone thought about it,

561
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:52,720
and decided to raise her in the troupe.

562
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,520
Because she was the youngest,

563
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:57,320
everyone called her Xiaomei.

564
00:27:57,360 --> 00:28:00,880
Xiaomei grew up with her older brothers and sister.

565
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,320
Although life was poor,

566
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:03,760
there was a lot of joy.

567
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:06,680
She was loved by her two older brothers

568
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:09,080
and had the company of her older sister, Yueyue.

569
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:11,200
The two sisters were inseparable.

570
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:13,280
They were like family to each other.

571
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:15,000
Unexpectedly,

572
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:17,120
Yueyue fell seriously ill.

573
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:19,000
The doctor said it was terminal.

574
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:22,440
Yueyue wanted to pass her unique magic tricks

575
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,810
on to her little sister.

576
00:28:24,120 --> 00:28:26,800
Her little sister adamantly refused to learn at first.

577
00:28:26,800 --> 00:28:28,160
She sought medical help everywhere,

578
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,840
hoping to cure Yueyue.

579
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,800
But Yueyue's condition only worsened.

580
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:33,920
Knowing her days were numbered, Yueyue

581
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:36,380
began to teach her little sister her skills.

582
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:38,640
Magic is an illusion,

583
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,080
which is sleight of hand.

584
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:42,020
As long as your hands are fast,

585
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:44,720
you can make the audience cheer for you.

586
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:45,820
But I'm clumsy.

587
00:28:45,840 --> 00:28:47,800
I can't learn my sister's tricks.

588
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,400
It doesn't matter.

589
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:51,600
You're so smart.

590
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,300
You will definitely learn it.

591
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:01,880
Little sister, look at the stars.

592
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:05,080
Making a wish upon a star is the most effective.

593
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:09,080
I hope before I leave,

594
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:12,120
I can watch Xiaomei perform one last time.

595
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:15,320
To fulfill Yueyue's wish,

596
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:17,520
Xiaomei studied hard

597
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:20,200
and finally learned how to do magic tricks.

598
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,880
In the audience,

599
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:24,120
the one applauding the loudest

600
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:26,520
was Yueyue, watching the show.

601
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:28,000
Troupe Leader Lu,

602
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:30,160
where did you find her back then?

603
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:33,760
It should be Yanzhi Alley in the North Market.

604
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:35,720
Yanzhi Alley.

605
00:29:35,760 --> 00:29:36,880
The answer is not rouge,

606
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,840
but Yanzhi Alley.

607
00:29:37,840 --> 00:29:39,760
Let's go. Hurry up.

608
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:47,520
Sir.

609
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:50,040
Have you seen a box this big with a copper clasp? Have you seen it?

610
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:50,920
No.

611
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,960
Sir, have you seen

612
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:01,080
a box this big with a copper clasp? What are you doing?

613
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:01,760
Go, go, go, go.

614
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:02,760
Okay, thank you.

615
00:30:02,800 --> 00:30:03,480
Sorry.

616
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:10,840
Jinglan.

617
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,120
Sulang.

618
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,340
There is a box here.

619
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:31,400
Formless and invisible, it wanders around,

620
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:33,520
caressing willow branches to dance gently.

621
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:35,850
It ruffles the lake into a thousand waves,

622
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:38,440
and sends floral fragrance past the pavilion.

623
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,680
Another riddle.

624
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:40,800
If we keep guessing,

625
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:43,000
our sister will only have her head left.

626
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,040
Strange.

627
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:54,160
Could our sister have already been killed?

628
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,490
What makes you say that?

629
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:59,740
A dead person's muscles lack elasticity and the ability to contract,

630
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:02,400
making the wound relatively flat,

631
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,800
just like this one.

632
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,000
As for a living person,

633
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,760
if their limbs are chopped off,

634
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:08,480
the muscles will contract,

635
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:10,480
leaving uneven wound edges.

636
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:13,040
And the blood color would be bright.

637
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,080
As for this one,

638
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:16,480
there is only a little blood loss.

639
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,680
When the severed limb was first found,

640
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,880
was it also like this?

641
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:23,000
No.

642
00:31:23,800 --> 00:31:26,520
What if the limb was chopped off right after death?

643
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:29,480
Would it match a severed limb chopped off from a living person?

644
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,800
It's hard to tell.

645
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:33,440
I see.

646
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:34,880
Jinglan.

647
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:36,720
You cleared up my last doubt.

648
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,120
Sulang.

649
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:40,040
I'll take you to the real killer.

